Package: fonts-karla
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Karla fonts
 Karla is a grotesque sans serif typeface family that
 supports languages that use the Latin script and the Tamil
 script. This is the Latin script part of the family, with
 Roman and Italic styles in two weights, Regular and Bold.
 .
 The Tamil parts are available from the Early Access page.
 .
 To contribute to the project contact Jonathan Pinhorn.

